        "Target": "\u30E9\u30F3\u30B4\u30B9\u30BF\u3068\u30AB\u30F3\u30BF\u30ED\u30B9\r\n\u5408\u8A08\uFF12\uFF10\u5339\u306E\u8A0E\u4F10",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Buggin\u0027 Out!",
        "Client": "Entomophobic Hunter",
        "Description": "Ew! EW! Get them away from me!\r\nGross, gross, GROSS! Like, why\r\ndidn\u0027t someone tell me the Jungle\r\nwould be literally CRAWLING with\r\nbugs? Monsters? OK. But, bugs?\r\nBUGS? HELLO! I did NOT sign up\r\nfor this, OK? Yuck.",
        "Target": "Slay a total of 20 Vespoid or Hornetaur",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Double Trouble",
        "Client": "Chasseur entomophobe",
        "Description": "Des Vespoid et des Hornetaur\r\nont surgi alors que j\u0027essayais\r\nd\u0027esquiver un monstre !\r\nDu coup, celui-ci\r\nm\u0027a mordu le derri\u00E8re !\r\nSi tu pouvais les \u00E9liminer...\r\nJ\u0027aime pas les morsures !",
        "Target": "Tuer un total de 20 Vespoid\r\nou Hornetaur",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Guai pungenti",
        "Client": "Cacciatrice entomofobica",
        "Description": "Mentre cercavo di schivare un\r\nmostro, ecco che arrivano dei\r\nVespoid e degli Hornetaur. E\r\nmentre ero distratta, la bestia\r\nmi ha morsicato il didietro.\r\nElimina quelle due specie\r\ne salva il mio sedere.",
        "Target": "Uccidi 20 Vespoid o Hornetaur in totale",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Insektenplage",
        "Client": "Entomophobischer J\u00E4ger",
        "Description": "Igitt! IGITT! Ekel-HAFT! Schaff\r\ndie weg von mir! Warum hat mir\r\ndenn niemand gesagt, dass es\r\nim Dschungel nur so wimmelt?\r\nMonster? Okay. Aber Insekten?\r\nKEINE INSEKTEN! Das mache ich\r\nnicht mit! Ich bin raus hier!",
        "Target": "Erlege insgesamt 20\r\nVespoiden oder Hornetauren",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "No lo ha bicho venir",
        "Client": "Cazadora entomof\u00F3bica",
        "Description": "\u00A1Qu\u00E9 asco! \u00A1\u00A1Qu\u00E9 ascooo!!\r\n\u00A1Que no se me acerquen! Puaj...\r\n\u00A1\u00BFPor qu\u00E9 nadie me avis\u00F3 de que\r\nla Jungla est\u00E1 llena de bichos?!\r\nMonstruos, vale, \u00A1\u00BFpero bichos?!\r\n\u00A1A m\u00ED nadie me avis\u00F3 de esto!",
        "Target": "Abate a un total de 20 Vespoid u\r\nHornetaur",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041F\u0440\u043E\u0431\u043B\u0435\u043C\u044B \u0441 \u043D\u0430\u0441\u0435\u043A\u043E\u043C\u044B\u043C\u0438",
